<div class="jumbotron">
  <br>
  <br>
  <h1 class="title">启程网</h1>
  <p class="slogan">完成了十几年的进修之路，我们终于要踏上真正的战场了。
  <br>
  <br>
  <strong>启程网</strong>为广大应届毕业战士们提供了各种企业的校招信息、招聘信息等。
  <br>
  <br>
  赶快在这里选择你的第一个副本，启程吧！
  </p>
  <br>
  <p class="lead"><a class="btn btn-lg btn-danger" href="/jobs">选择副本</a></p>
</div>
<hr/>
<h1>最新副本</h1>
<div class="dropdown clearfix pull-right">
    <button class="btn btn-default dropdown-toggle" type="button" id="dropdownMenuDivider" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="true">
      排序
        <span class="caret"></span>
    </button>
    <ul class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenuDivider">
        <li>
          <%= link_to("按照薪资下限排序", jobs_path(:order => "by_lower_bound")) %>
        </li>
        <li>
            <%= link_to("按照薪资上限排序", jobs_path(:order => "by_upper_bound")) %>

        </li>
        <li>
          <%= link_to("按照发表时间排序", jobs_path ) %>

        </li>
    </ul>
</div>
<br>
<br>
<table class="table table-boldered table-striped table-bordered table-hover">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <td>
                职缺</td>
            <td>薪资下限</td>
            <td>薪资上限</td>
            <td>刊登时间</td>
        </tr>

    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <% @jobs.each do |job| %>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <%= link_to(job.title, job_path(job)) %>
            </td>
            <td>
                <%= job.wage_lower_bound %>
            </td>
            <td>
                <%= job.wage_upper_bound %>
            </td>
            <td>
                <%= job.created_at %>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <% end %>
    </tbody>

</table>
